                          "content": "Wire Google OAuth as a second sign-in method alongside email + password. The button lives on the sign-in screen above the email field; clicking it redirects the user to the OAuth consent screen, then back to our callback. On callback, we exchange the code for an ID token, verify the token, and either sign the user in (if a matching account exists) or auto-link to an existing email/password user with the same email.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.55,
                          "fontFamily": "$--font-sans",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
